      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, i need help writing a rejection email for a candidate. They made it all the way to the final round for a Senior DevOps Engineer position here in Austin, but we decided to go with someone who has a bit more experience with Kubernetes orchestration. The candidate was actually really impressive and had great soft skills, so i want the email to be professional and kind, but very clear that we aren't moving forward with them right now. Can you help me draft something?",
