      "content": "Subject: Your Application for Senior DevOps Engineer Position\n\nDear [Candidate's Name],\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I wanted to take a moment to thank you for your interest in the Senior DevOps Engineer position at our Austin-based company. We were truly impressed by your skills, experience, and the enthusiasm you brought to the final round of interviews.\n\nAfter careful consideration, we have decided to move forward with a candidate who has a bit more experience with Kubernetes orchestration. This decision was not easy, as you were a strong contender and your soft skills were truly commendable. We believe that your talents and abilities would have been a great asset to our team, and we appreciate the time and effort you invested in the application process.\n\nWe encourage you to apply for future opportunities that align with your skills and experience. We wish you the best of luck in your job search and future endeavors.\n\nThank you once again for your interest in our company.\n\nBest regards,\n\n[Your Name]\n[Your Position]\n[Company Name]",
