      "content": "thanks. it looks good but it a bit too generic i think. can we make it sound a little more personal and warm? like, acknowledging that interviewing for these roles is a lot of work and we really value the time they spent with us. maybe add a line about how they should definitely keep an eye on our careers page for future roles specifically in the DevOps space. can you try another version with that tone?",
